{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 19,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 482.597,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.786,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Lord commanded me,",
      "verse": "19:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.966,
      "end": 5.706,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore I did make plates of ore",
      "verse": "19:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 5.886,
      "end": 9.648,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I might engraven upon them the record of my people.",
      "verse": "19:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 9.828,
      "end": 12.15,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And upon the plates which I made",
      "verse": "19:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 12.33,
      "end": 14.977,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I did engraven the record of my father,",
      "verse": "19:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 15.157,
      "end": 17.99,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also our journeyings in the wilderness,",
      "verse": "19:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 18.17,
      "end": 20.26,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the prophecies of my father;",
      "verse": "19:1",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 20.44,
      "end": 24.759,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also many of mine own prophecies have I engraven upon them.",
      "verse": "19:1",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 25.439,
      "end": 28.179,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I knew not at the time when I made them",
      "verse": "19:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 28.359,
      "end": 31.796,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I should be commanded of the Lord to make these plates;",
      "verse": "19:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 31.976,
      "end": 34.437,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, the record of my father,",
      "verse": "19:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 34.617,
      "end": 37.728,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the genealogy of his fathers, and the more part",
      "verse": "19:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 37.908,
      "end": 40.462,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of all our proceedings in the wilderness",
      "verse": "19:2",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 40.642,
      "end": 45.007,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are engraven upon those first plates of which I have spoken;",
      "verse": "19:2",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 45.187,
      "end": 50.946,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, the things which transpired before I made these plates are, of a truth,",
      "verse": "19:2",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 51.126,
      "end": 54.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "more particularly made mention upon the first plates.",
      "verse": "19:2",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 55.15,
      "end": 58.494,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after I had made these plates by way of commandment,",
      "verse": "19:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 58.674,
      "end": 61.182,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I, Nephi, received a commandment",
      "verse": "19:3",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 61.362,
      "end": 63.823,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the ministry and the prophecies,",
      "verse": "19:3",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 64.003,
      "end": 66.511,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the more plain and precious parts of them,",
      "verse": "19:3",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 66.691,
      "end": 69.059,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should be written upon these plates;",
      "verse": "19:3",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 69.239,
      "end": 71.282,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that the things which were written",
      "verse": "19:3",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 71.462,
      "end": 74.527,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should be kept for the instruction of my people,",
      "verse": "19:3",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 74.707,
      "end": 76.611,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who should possess the land,",
      "verse": "19:3",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 76.791,
      "end": 79.113,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also for other wise purposes,",
      "verse": "19:3",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 79.293,
      "end": 81.801,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which purposes are known unto the Lord.",
      "verse": "19:3",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 82.481,
      "end": 86.8,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I, Nephi, did make a record upon the other plates,",
      "verse": "19:4",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 86.98,
      "end": 88.513,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which gives a account,",
      "verse": "19:4",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 88.693,
      "end": 91.851,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or which gives a greater account of the wars",
      "verse": "19:4",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 92.031,
      "end": 94.771,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and contentions and destructions of my people.",
      "verse": "19:4",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 94.951,
      "end": 97.784,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And this have I done, and commanded my people",
      "verse": "19:4",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 97.964,
      "end": 100.658,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "what they should do after I was gone;",
      "verse": "19:4",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 100.838,
      "end": 104.971,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that these plates should be handed down from one generation to another,",
      "verse": "19:4",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 105.151,
      "end": 107.612,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or from one prophet to another,",
      "verse": "19:4",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 107.792,
      "end": 110.021,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until further commandments of the Lord.",
      "verse": "19:4",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 110.701,
      "end": 115.809,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And an account of my making these plates shall be given hereafter; and then, behold,",
      "verse": "19:5",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 115.989,
      "end": 120.819,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I proceed according to that which I have spoken; and this I do",
      "verse": "19:5",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 120.999,
      "end": 125.318,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the more sacred things may be kept for the knowledge of my people.",
      "verse": "19:5",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 125.998,
      "end": 129.202,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nevertheless, I do not write anything upon plates",
      "verse": "19:6",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 129.382,
      "end": 131.704,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save it be that I think it be sacred.",
      "verse": "19:6",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 131.884,
      "end": 135.042,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, if I do err, even did they err of old;",
      "verse": "19:6",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 135.222,
      "end": 138.194,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "not that I would excuse myself because of other men,",
      "verse": "19:6",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 138.374,
      "end": 140.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but because of the weakness which is in me,",
      "verse": "19:6",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 141.015,
      "end": 142.501,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the flesh,",
      "verse": "19:6",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 142.681,
      "end": 144.26,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I would excuse myself.",
      "verse": "19:6",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 144.94,
      "end": 150.373,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For the things which some men esteem to be of great worth, both to the body and soul,",
      "verse": "19:7",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 150.553,
      "end": 153.618,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "others set at naught and trample under their feet.",
      "verse": "19:7",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 153.798,
      "end": 156.166,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, even the very God of Israel",
      "verse": "19:7",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 156.346,
      "end": 158.343,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "do men trample under their feet;",
      "verse": "19:7",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 158.523,
      "end": 160.52,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I say, trample under their feet",
      "verse": "19:7",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 160.7,
      "end": 164.137,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but I would speak in other words\u2014 they set him at naught,",
      "verse": "19:7",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 164.317,
      "end": 166.871,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and hearken not to the voice of his counsels.",
      "verse": "19:7",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 167.551,
      "end": 169.037,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold he cometh,",
      "verse": "19:8",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 169.217,
      "end": 171.4,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the words of the angel,",
      "verse": "19:8",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 171.58,
      "end": 173.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in six hundred years",
      "verse": "19:8",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 173.478,
      "end": 175.893,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the time my father left Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "19:8",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 176.573,
      "end": 178.013,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the world,",
      "verse": "19:9",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 178.193,
      "end": 180.004,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of their iniquity,",
      "verse": "19:9",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 180.184,
      "end": 182.785,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall judge him to be a thing of naught;",
      "verse": "19:9",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 182.965,
      "end": 184.915,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore they scourge him,",
      "verse": "19:9",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 185.095,
      "end": 186.767,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he suffereth it;",
      "verse": "19:9",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 186.947,
      "end": 188.387,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they smite him,",
      "verse": "19:9",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 188.567,
      "end": 190.239,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he suffereth it.",
      "verse": "19:9",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 190.419,
      "end": 192.137,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, they spit upon him,",
      "verse": "19:9",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 192.317,
      "end": 194.082,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he suffereth it,",
      "verse": "19:9",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 194.262,
      "end": 196.352,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of his loving kindness",
      "verse": "19:9",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 196.532,
      "end": 199.597,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and his long-suffering towards the children of men.",
      "verse": "19:9",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 200.277,
      "end": 202.227,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the God of our fathers,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 202.407,
      "end": 206.029,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who were led out of Egypt, out of bondage,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 206.209,
      "end": 209.32,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also were preserved in the wilderness by him,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 209.5,
      "end": 213.447,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, the God of Abraham, and of Isaac, and the God of Jacob,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 213.627,
      "end": 215.067,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yieldeth himself,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 215.247,
      "end": 217.43,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the words of the angel,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 217.61,
      "end": 221.325,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as a man, into the hands of wicked men, to be lifted up,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 221.505,
      "end": 225.034,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the words of Zenock, and to be crucified,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 225.214,
      "end": 227.49,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the words of Neum,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 227.67,
      "end": 229.667,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to be buried in a sepulchre,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 229.847,
      "end": 231.937,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the words of Zenos,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 232.117,
      "end": 235.414,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he spake concerning the three days of darkness,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 235.594,
      "end": 238.241,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which should be a sign given of his death",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 238.421,
      "end": 241.625,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto those who should inhabit the isles of the sea,",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 241.805,
      "end": 245.938,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "more especially given unto those who are of the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "19:10",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 246.618,
      "end": 248.522,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For thus spake the prophet:",
      "verse": "19:11",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 248.702,
      "end": 252.557,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "The Lord God surely shall visit all the house of Israel at that day,",
      "verse": "19:11",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 252.737,
      "end": 254.316,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "some with his voice,",
      "verse": "19:11",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 254.496,
      "end": 256.679,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of their righteousness,",
      "verse": "19:11",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 256.859,
      "end": 259.367,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto their great joy and salvation,",
      "verse": "19:11",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 259.547,
      "end": 263.169,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and others with the thunderings and the lightnings of his power,",
      "verse": "19:11",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 263.349,
      "end": 265.067,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by tempest, by fire,",
      "verse": "19:11",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 265.247,
      "end": 267.848,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and by smoke, and vapor of darkness,",
      "verse": "19:11",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 268.028,
      "end": 270.257,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and by the opening of the earth,",
      "verse": "19:11",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 270.437,
      "end": 272.759,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and by mountains which shall be carried up.",
      "verse": "19:11",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 273.439,
      "end": 277.154,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all these things must surely come, saith the prophet Zenos.",
      "verse": "19:12",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 277.334,
      "end": 279.749,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the rocks of the earth must rend;",
      "verse": "19:12",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 279.929,
      "end": 282.53,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and because of the groanings of the earth,",
      "verse": "19:12",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 282.71,
      "end": 285.357,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many of the kings of the isles of the sea",
      "verse": "19:12",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 285.537,
      "end": 289.066,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be wrought upon by the Spirit of God, to exclaim:",
      "verse": "19:12",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 289.246,
      "end": 291.15,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "The God of nature suffers.",
      "verse": "19:12",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 291.83,
      "end": 295.406,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And as for those who are at Jerusalem, saith the prophet,",
      "verse": "19:13",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 295.586,
      "end": 297.862,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be scourged by all people,",
      "verse": "19:13",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 298.042,
      "end": 300.55,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because they crucify the God of Israel,",
      "verse": "19:13",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 300.73,
      "end": 302.634,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and turn their hearts aside,",
      "verse": "19:13",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 302.814,
      "end": 305.09,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "rejecting signs and wonders,",
      "verse": "19:13",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 305.27,
      "end": 308.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the power and glory of the God of Israel.",
      "verse": "19:13",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 308.829,
      "end": 311.987,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And because they turn their hearts aside, saith the prophet,",
      "verse": "19:14",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 312.167,
      "end": 314.861,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have despised the Holy One of Israel,",
      "verse": "19:14",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 315.041,
      "end": 317.735,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall wander in the flesh, and perish,",
      "verse": "19:14",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 317.915,
      "end": 320.33,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and become a hiss and a byword,",
      "verse": "19:14",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 320.51,
      "end": 322.832,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and be hated among all nations.",
      "verse": "19:14",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 323.512,
      "end": 326.856,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nevertheless, when that day cometh, saith the prophet,",
      "verse": "19:15",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 327.036,
      "end": 329.683,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they no more turn aside their hearts",
      "verse": "19:15",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 329.863,
      "end": 332.185,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "against the Holy One of Israel,",
      "verse": "19:15",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 332.365,
      "end": 336.452,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then will he remember the covenants which he made to their fathers.",
      "verse": "19:15",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 337.132,
      "end": 340.058,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, then will he remember the isles of the sea;",
      "verse": "19:16",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 340.238,
      "end": 344.836,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and all the people who are of the house of Israel, will I gather in,",
      "verse": "19:16",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 345.016,
      "end": 346.409,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith the Lord,",
      "verse": "19:16",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 346.589,
      "end": 349.422,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the words of the prophet Zenos,",
      "verse": "19:16",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 349.602,
      "end": 352.481,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the four quarters of the earth.",
      "verse": "19:16",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 353.161,
      "end": 354.833,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, and all the earth",
      "verse": "19:17",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 355.013,
      "end": 358.45,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall see the salvation of the Lord, saith the prophet;",
      "verse": "19:17",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 358.63,
      "end": 362.067,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "every nation, kindred, tongue and people shall be blessed.",
      "verse": "19:17",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 362.747,
      "end": 366.044,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, have written these things unto my people,",
      "verse": "19:18",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 366.224,
      "end": 368.778,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that perhaps I might persuade them",
      "verse": "19:18",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 368.958,
      "end": 371.698,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they would remember the Lord their Redeemer.",
      "verse": "19:18",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 372.378,
      "end": 375.582,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I speak unto all the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "19:19",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 375.762,
      "end": 378.641,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it so be that they should obtain these things.",
      "verse": "19:19",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 379.321,
      "end": 382.061,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, I have workings in the spirit,",
      "verse": "19:20",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 382.241,
      "end": 383.634,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which doth weary me",
      "verse": "19:20",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 383.814,
      "end": 385.95,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even that all my joints are weak,",
      "verse": "19:20",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 386.13,
      "end": 388.127,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for those who are at Jerusalem;",
      "verse": "19:20",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 388.307,
      "end": 390.629,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for had not the Lord been merciful,",
      "verse": "19:20",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 390.809,
      "end": 392.945,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to show unto me concerning them,",
      "verse": "19:20",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 393.125,
      "end": 395.308,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even as he had prophets of old,",
      "verse": "19:20",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 395.488,
      "end": 397.206,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I should have perished also.",
      "verse": "19:20",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 397.886,
      "end": 402.205,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he surely did show unto the prophets of old all things concerning them;",
      "verse": "19:21",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 402.385,
      "end": 405.404,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also he did show unto many concerning us;",
      "verse": "19:21",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 405.584,
      "end": 407.395,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, it must needs be",
      "verse": "19:21",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 407.575,
      "end": 409.572,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we know concerning them",
      "verse": "19:21",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 409.752,
      "end": 412.724,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they are written upon the plates of brass.",
      "verse": "19:21",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 413.404,
      "end": 418.28,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now it came to pass that I, Nephi, did teach my brethren these things;",
      "verse": "19:22",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 418.46,
      "end": 421.989,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it came to pass that I did read many things to them,",
      "verse": "19:22",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 422.169,
      "end": 425.884,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were engraven upon the plates of brass,",
      "verse": "19:22",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 426.064,
      "end": 429.501,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might know concerning the doings of the Lord",
      "verse": "19:22",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 429.681,
      "end": 432.189,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in other lands, among people of old.",
      "verse": "19:22",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 432.869,
      "end": 435.33,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I did read many things unto them",
      "verse": "19:23",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 435.51,
      "end": 438.018,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were written in the books of Moses;",
      "verse": "19:23",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 438.198,
      "end": 441.217,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but that I might more fully persuade them",
      "verse": "19:23",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 441.397,
      "end": 443.533,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to believe in the Lord their Redeemer",
      "verse": "19:23",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 443.713,
      "end": 445.338,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I did read unto them",
      "verse": "19:23",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 445.518,
      "end": 448.026,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that which was written by the prophet Isaiah;",
      "verse": "19:23",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 448.206,
      "end": 451.039,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I did liken all scriptures unto us,",
      "verse": "19:23",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 451.219,
      "end": 454.098,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it might be for our profit and learning.",
      "verse": "19:23",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 454.778,
      "end": 457.007,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore I spake unto them, saying:",
      "verse": "19:24",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 457.187,
      "end": 459.323,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Hear ye the words of the prophet,",
      "verse": "19:24",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 459.503,
      "end": 462.429,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye who are a remnant of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "19:24",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 462.609,
      "end": 464.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a branch who have been broken off;",
      "verse": "19:24",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 465.065,
      "end": 467.155,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "hear ye the words of the prophet,",
      "verse": "19:24",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 467.335,
      "end": 471.236,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were written unto all the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "19:24",
      "lineIndex": 161
    },
    {
      "start": 471.416,
      "end": 473.692,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and liken them unto yourselves,",
      "verse": "19:24",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 473.872,
      "end": 476.705,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that ye may have hope as well as your brethren",
      "verse": "19:24",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 476.885,
      "end": 479.161,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from whom ye have been broken off;",
      "verse": "19:24",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 479.341,
      "end": 481.942,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for after this manner has the prophet written.",
      "verse": "19:24",
      "lineIndex": 165
    }
  ]
}